<!-- wp:details {"style":{"border":{"bottom":{"color":"#E5E7EE","style":"solid","width":"1px"}},"spacing":{"padding":{"top":"22px","bottom":"22px"}},"typography":{"fontSize":"17px","fontWeight":"500","letterSpacing":"-0.01em"}}} -->
